high_descs: Turn around and face the green counter on your left.
Take the rag off the green counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the drawer on your left.
Place the rag in the drawer in front of you and close the drawer.
Turn right then face the counter with the rag on the left.
Take the rag off of the green counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the drawer on your right.
Place the rag inside of the drawer in front of you.
Turn around and face the counter on the left.
Pick up the red cloth from the left side of the counter.
Hold the cloth and take a few steps to the right.
Open the top drawer and place the cloth inside. Shut the drawer.
Look up to the counter above the drawer.
Pick up the cloth on the right side of the counter.
Hold the cloth and look around the room.
Open the drawer below, and place the cloth inside. Shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two cloths to the drawer.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the rag from the counter.
Turn left, move to the counter right of the sink.
Put the rag in the drawer.
Turn right, move to the counter right of the sink.
Pick up the rag from the counter.
Move to the counter, right of the sink.
Put the rag in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place two rags into a drawer.
